oracle.ateam.sample.mobile.v2.persistence.manager

Interface PersistenceManager

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RemotePersistenceManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPersistenceManager, AbstractRemotePersistenceManager, DataControlPersistenceManager, DBPersistenceManager, MCSPersistenceManager, MCSStoragePersistenceManager, RestADFBCXMLPersistenceManager, RestJSONPersistenceManager, RestPersistenceManager, RestXMLPersistenceManager

    public interface PersistenceManager
    Interface that provides basic CRUD operations for a given entity instance. You can plug in a local and remote PersistenceManager implementation in your concrete subclasse of EntityCRUDService to handle local data storage as well as synchronization with a remote data source.
    See Also:
    EntityCRUDService
